<br>
Go Slash, you are resisted by Warriors, Thanes, Skalds, Healers and Shamans.  You take down zerkers, sbs, hunters and savages like no tommorow.  You also slaughter all the scale wearers, but you have problems with Nightshades, Blademasters and the rare Battlebard. <br>
<br>
Seemingly they even themselves out pretty well on paper.  My slash merc has a gay old time in RvR and my memories of the 1v1 duels with the Hibbie tanks on my 50/50/28 slasher merc on my old account are quite vivid.<br>
<br>
I've never tried a crush merc, but my crush armsman does very well in PvE and ok in Abermenai(Which isn't too hard with all the newbs).  All the styles that key off of the taunt look like they would work well since in groups an armsman should spam their taunt style for the first few rounds.<br>
